prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "Register users, patients or caregivers to access all resources",
      "evidence_quote": "this functionality acts as a membership functionality that allows the users, patients or caregivers to register into this website to access all the resources."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Authenticate user for access permissions",
      "evidence_quote": "Login – this functionality authenticates the user to provide access permissions."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Provide access to all options available on the website",
      "evidence_quote": "Facilities – this functionality allows us to access all the options available on the website."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "End user access to the website",
      "evidence_quote": "Logout – this functionality ends the access to the website."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Allow users to purchase insurance or pay for healthcare services consumed",
      "evidence_quote": "Finance – this functionality allows to purchase insurance, or to pay for healthcare services consumed."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Provide details of all diseases",
      "evidence_quote": "Health A–Z – this functionality provides details of all the diseases."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Offer online delivery of medicines",
      "evidence_quote": "Drugs and supplements – this functionality provides online delivery of medicines. This functionality takes the doctor’s statement for the issue of medicine and the patient’s willingness to buy it online."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Provide health awareness and threats prevailing",
      "evidence_quote": "News and experts – this functionality provides health awareness and threats that are prevailing."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Deal with payment for services consumed",
      "evidence_quote": "Payment – this functionality deals with the payment for the services consumed. This functionality is split into two sub-functions namely, payment for doctors, for the services issued and payment for online med-delivery."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Collect user reviews for the website",
      "evidence_quote": "Feedback – this functionality collects user reviews for this website."
    }
  ]
}

